<h2 id="a-thriving-and-growing-online-community">A thriving and growing online community</h2>
<p>A core pillar of ours is to provide on-going support and a sense of belonging amongst our community. Our Slack group is a space that is open to the public where design students, enthusiasts, professionals, and educators, can engage in conversation. We offer a range of groups that include career development, events, networking, and more.
